data.description: Come check out this beauty. Located in ideal District 20 schools.This home sits on a huge lot with extra parking. Very close to schools, parks, shopping & walking trails but still tucked away into a quiet neighborhood. The baths are completely updated, and the kitchen is remodeled. Included is a new microwave, dishwasher stove and refrigerator. Open and bright with beam ceilings and fireplace, great for entertaining. Walk out to the deck and enjoy the Colorado air. Upgrades and extras to include A/C, new thermostat, fresh paint indoor and out. Smooth ceilings, new garage door, new flooring and EV Charger. Bonus is the durable tile roof and walk out lower levelThere is an upgraded electrical box to 200 amp and hot tub ready. New landscaping front and back, new front fence sprinklers and sliding doors. New water heater, gutter drainage system, fixtures and can lighting through out the home. Everything is included even a new washer and dryer. Make this your new home today!
